      "content": "Sure, I can help with that. Here's a draft for the transition guide:\n\n---\n\n**Transition Guide for New Customer Interface**\n\nDear Valued Client,\n\nWe are excited to announce that we will be upgrading our customer interface to a new, more efficient model, starting tomorrow at midnight. This upgrade is designed to enhance your experience by making interactions 20% faster and more responsive, especially during peak hours.\n\n**What to Expect:**\n\n1. **Transition Time:** The switch will occur at midnight, during which our system will be temporarily unavailable. We anticipate the transition to take approximately 10-15 minutes.\n2. **Interface Changes:** You may notice slight changes in the layout and design. These changes are aimed at improving usability and functionality.\n3. **New Features:** The new interface will include several new features to enhance your experience. We recommend exploring and familiarizing yourself with these features once the transition is complete.\n4. **Support:** Should you encounter any issues or have questions during the transition, our support team is available 24/7 to assist you.\n\nWe appreciate your understanding and cooperation as we work to provide you with an even better experience. Thank you for being a valued client.\n\nBest regards,\n[Your Company Name]\n\n---",
