      "content": "thanks for the draft. it looks pretty standard, maybe a bit too generic though. since our clients are high-net-worth individuals, they expect a lot of nuance. one thing i'm worried about is that the new model might lack the specific \"personal touch\" and deep travel expertise you've built up. can you add a section that explains why they might notice a difference in the quality of the recommendations or the level of personalization they receive after the switch?",
